<br>
&quot;This is fucking sick. I don't do animals!&quot; I snarled back at him, forgetting and no longer caring about trying to get their help now. I was ready to kill every last one of them if only I could get my damn arms free from their grasp. I also realised very quickly that using the term &quot;animal&quot; was a huge mistake. It felt like I was outside of my body for I was no longer in control of it as I was held by the three behind me. Against my will my legs were undressed and parted as I was held horizontal and about waist high. &quot;You'll pay for this I so fucking SWEAR!&quot; I thrashed about vainly as their leader moved between my legs. Blood tricked from my lips as I gritted my teeth and closed my eyes when I felt my womanhood violated by his very large sweaty length. I do not know if it was from the pain or from the intermittant lose of conscienceness that I had but their voices became distant as I passed out.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~ ~ Some Time Later ~ ~</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Zabian... looks like she is coming around...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Man you made her pass out... wonder how she feels... to bad she won't know how long you fucked her...&quot; voices rang dimly in my head as I slowly came to. My eyes struggled open only to view blurry images and there was a pain deep in my stomach between my legs. Oh that <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>were</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> leader was going to die, that stupid piece of shit that he was. I had never been raped since I was twelve years old and that was when I had learned of what I was. Death had met the men shortly afterwards from my hands and I was already planning the fate of these creatures.<br>
