I sighed deeply as I touched the warm water with my finger to test its warmth. &quot;Of course I know now... but innocence was stripped from me as they all took me long after I had passed out from pain. I woke up next to my mother who never did wake up when I called to her... fucking bastards! I felt an anger burn through me, giving me power beyond anything I felt possible... I had fangs in my mouth and such a hatred in my heart that I hunted down the last of those men and killed them all. Their blood fueled me on...&quot;<br>
